<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %> - Thầy Tài Toeic
    </title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Sora:wght@600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f6f2eb;
            --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, .94);
            --line: rgba(17, 24, 39, .08);
            --text: #1f2937;
            --muted: #667085;
            --brand: #c91f30;
            --brand-soft: rgba(201, 31, 48, .08);
            --dark: #111
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Be Vietnam Pro", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(201, 31, 48, .08), transparent 24%), radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(183, 177, 241, .18), transparent 25%), linear-gradient(180deg, #fbf8f4 0%, #f6f2eb 100%)
        }

        body.menu-open {
            overflow: hidden
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit
        }

        .s-header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .06)
        }

        .s-wrap {
            width: min(1780px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto
        }

        .s-bar {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 8px 0
        }

        .s-brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            flex: 0 0 auto
        }

        .s-brand-mark {
            width: 72px;
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(201, 31, 48, .12);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, .9) 0%, rgba(255, 241, 243, .92) 100%);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(201, 31, 48, .08);
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .s-brand-mark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
            padding: 3px
        }

        .s-brand-copy {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1px
        }

        .s-brand-copy strong {
            font-family: "Sora", "Be Vietnam Pro", sans-serif;
            font-size: .82rem;
            line-height: 1.08;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            color: #b01224;
            text-transform: uppercase
        }

        .s-brand-copy span {
            display: none;
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: var(--muted)
        }

        .s-nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2px;
            min-width: 0;
            padding-inline: 6px;
            overflow: visible
        }

        .s-nav::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none
        }

        .s-link {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            padding: 10px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: .83rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            white-space: nowrap;
            transition: .2s ease
        }

        .s-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            color: #111827;
            background: rgba(17, 24, 39, .04)
        }

        .s-link.active {
            color: #111827;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, .08)
        }

        .s-link.active::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 14px;
            right: 14px;
            bottom: 2px;
            height: 3px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #3b82f6
        }

        .s-link-label-full {
            display: inline
        }

        .s-link-label-short {
            display: none
        }

        .s-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            justify-self: end
        }

        .s-badge {
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 7px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--brand-soft);
            color: var(--brand);
            font-size: .82rem;
            font-weight: 700
        }

        .s-profile {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(17, 24, 39, .04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .06);
            transition: transform .2s ease, background .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease
        }

        .s-profile:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, .08);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(17, 24, 39, .08)
        }

        .s-profile-meta {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2px;
            max-width: 112px;
            padding-left: 4px
        }

        .s-profile-meta strong,
        .s-profile-meta span {
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap
        }

        .s-profile-meta strong {
            font-size: .84rem;
            line-height: 1.1
        }

        .s-profile-meta span {
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: var(--muted)
        }

        .s-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #374151 100%);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 800;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(17, 24, 39, .22)
        }

        .s-logout {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: .94rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(17, 17, 17, .16);
            transition: transform .2s ease
        }

        .s-logout:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px)
        }

        .s-logout-quick {
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 0 14px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, .14);
            background: rgba(254, 242, 242, .98);
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: .88rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            white-space: nowrap;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(220, 38, 38, .10)
        }

        .s-logout-quick svg {
            flex: 0 0 auto
        }

        .s-menu {
            display: none;
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .08);
            background: #fff;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center
        }

        .s-mobile {
            display: none;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 120;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .06);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .98);
            max-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
            overflow-y: auto;
            overscroll-behavior: contain
        }

        body.menu-open .s-mobile {
            display: block
        }
        body.menu-open .s-header {
            z-index: 140
        }
        body.menu-open .eng-fixed-left,
        body.menu-open .eng-fixed-stack {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none
        }

        .s-mobile-inner {
            width: min(1380px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 14px 0 18px;
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px
        }

        .s-mobile-account {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .08);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248, 250, 252, .98) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, .98) 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(17, 24, 39, .08)
        }

        .s-mobile-profile {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: inherit
        }

        .s-mobile-profile-copy {
            display: grid;
            gap: 4px;
            min-width: 0
        }

        .s-mobile-profile-copy strong {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: .96rem;
            line-height: 1.2
        }

        .s-mobile-profile-copy span {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: .8rem;
            line-height: 1.4
        }

        .s-mobile-actions {
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px
        }

        .s-mobile .s-link,
        .s-mobile .s-logout {
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
            touch-action: manipulation
        }

        .s-brand,
        .s-link,
        .s-profile,
        .s-logout,
        .s-logout-quick,
        .s-menu,
        .s-mobile-profile {
            touch-action: manipulation;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent
        }

        .s-stage {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 80px)
        }

        .s-stage :is(h1, h2) {
            font-family: "Sora", "Be Vietnam Pro", sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7a59 0%, #ff5d8f 46%, #ffb14a 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .s-flash {
            width: min(1380px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 18px auto 0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px
        }

        .s-flash-card {
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .9);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(17, 24, 39, .06)
        }

        .s-flash-card.success {
            color: #166534;
            border-color: rgba(22, 101, 52, .12)
        }

        .s-flash-card.error {
            color: #b91c1c;
            border-color: rgba(185, 28, 28, .12)
        }

        .s-flash-card.info {
            color: #1d4ed8;
            border-color: rgba(29, 78, 216, .12)
        }

        .s-footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .95);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .06)
        }

        .s-footer-inner {
            width: min(1380px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 38px 0 28px
        }

        .s-footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr 1.1fr;
            gap: 28px
        }

        .s-footer-col h3 {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-family: "Sora", "Be Vietnam Pro", sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            letter-spacing: -.02em
        }

        .s-footer-col p,
        .s-footer-col a {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            color: #2563eb;
            line-height: 1.55
        }

        .s-footer-col .lead {
            color: #4b5563
        }

        .s-footer-col strong {
            color: #111827
        }

        .s-legal {
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding-top: 18px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, .06);
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: .95rem
        }

        @media (max-width:1780px) {

            .s-badge,
            .s-brand-copy span {
                display: none
            }

            .s-link {
                padding: 10px 6px;
                font-size: .81rem
            }

            .s-profile-meta {
                max-width: 112px
            }

            .s-logout {
                padding: 10px 12px;
                font-size: .9rem
            }
        }

        @media (max-width:1620px) {
            .s-bar {
                gap: 7px
            }

            .s-brand {
                gap: 8px
            }

            .s-brand-mark {
                width: 66px;
                height: 42px
            }

            .s-brand-copy strong {
                font-size: .76rem
            }

            .s-link {
                padding: 9px 4px;
                font-size: .78rem
            }

            .s-profile {
                gap: 6px
            }

            .s-profile-meta {
                max-width: 96px
            }

            .s-profile-meta strong {
                font-size: .8rem
            }

            .s-avatar {
                width: 38px;
                height: 38px
            }

            .s-logout {
                padding: 9px 11px;
                font-size: .86rem
            }
        }

        @media (max-width:1520px) {
            .s-nav,
            .s-profile-meta,
            .s-logout {
                display: none
            }

            .s-logout-quick,
            .s-menu {
                display: inline-flex
            }
        }

        @media (max-width:1440px) {

            .s-nav,
            .s-badge,
            .s-profile-meta,
            .s-logout {
                display: none
            }

            .s-logout-quick,
            .s-menu {
                display: inline-flex
            }

            .s-footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr))
            }
        }

        @media (max-width:720px) {

            .s-wrap,
            .s-flash,
            .s-footer-inner,
            .s-mobile-inner {
                width: min(100% - 20px, 1380px)
            }

            .s-brand-copy span {
                display: none
            }

            .s-logout-quick {
                min-width: 46px;
                padding: 0 12px;
                gap: 6px;
                font-size: .82rem
            }

            .s-footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <% const normalizePath=(value)=> {
        const raw = String(value || '/').split('?')[0].split('#')[0];
        const trimmed = raw.replace(/\/+$/, '');
        return trimmed || '/';
        };

        const safeBaseUrl = typeof baseUrl !== 'undefined' ? baseUrl : '';
        const buildHref = (path) => `${safeBaseUrl}${path}`;
        const currentRoute = normalizePath(typeof currentPath !== 'undefined' ? currentPath : '/');

        const safeSuccessMessages = typeof success_msg !== 'undefined' ? success_msg : [];
        const safeErrorMessages = typeof error_msg !== 'undefined' ? error_msg : [];
        const safeInfoMessages = typeof error !== 'undefined' ? error : [];

        const brandLogo = 'https://i.postimg.cc/P5r5F9Mt/logo.jpg';

        const safeStudentName =
        typeof studentName !== 'undefined' && studentName
        ? studentName
        : 'Học viên';

        const studentInitial = safeStudentName.trim().charAt(0).toUpperCase() || 'H';

        const navItems = [
        { label: 'Trang chủ', href: buildHref('/'), matches: ['/'] },
        { label: 'Classroom', shortLabel: 'Classroom', href: buildHref('/student/classroom'), matches: ['/student/classroom'] },
        { label: 'Thi Thử Full Test', href: buildHref('/placement-tests'), matches: ['/placement-tests', '/test-start',
        '/test-result'] },
        { label: 'Luyện Tập Theo Part', shortLabel: 'Theo Part', href: buildHref('/student/practice/parts'), matches:
        ['/student/practice/parts'] },
        { label: 'Luyện Tập Reading', shortLabel: 'Reading', href: buildHref('/student/practice/reading'), matches:
        ['/student/practice/reading'] },
        { label: 'Nghe - Chép chính tả', shortLabel: 'Nghe - Chép', href: buildHref('/student/dictation'), matches:
        ['/student/dictation'] },
        { label: 'Khóa học', href: buildHref('/student/courses'), matches: ['/student/courses'] },
        { label: 'Lịch Khai Giảng', href: buildHref('/student/schedule'), matches: ['/student/schedule'] },
        { label: 'Liên Hệ', href: buildHref('/student/contact'), matches: ['/student/contact'] },
        { label: 'Góp Ý', href: buildHref('/student/feedback'), matches: ['/student/feedback'] },
        { label: 'Đăng ký khóa học', shortLabel: 'Đăng ký', href: buildHref('/register-course'), matches:
        ['/register-course', '/payment'] }
        ];

        const isActive = (item) => (item.matches || []).some((target) => {
        const normalized = normalizePath(safeBaseUrl + target);
        if (normalized === '/') return currentRoute === '/';
        return currentRoute === normalized || currentRoute.startsWith(normalized + '/');
        });
        %>

        <header class="s-header">
            <div class="s-wrap s-bar">
                <a href="<%= buildHref('/') %>" class="s-brand">
                    <span class="s-brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
                        <img src="<%= brandLogo %>" alt="Logo Thầy Tài Toeic">
                    </span>
                    <span class="s-brand-copy">
                        <strong>THẦY TÀI TOEIC</strong>
                        <span>Luyện thi và học trực tuyến</span>
                    </span>
                </a>

                <nav class="s-nav" aria-label="Điều hướng học viên">
                    <% navItems.forEach((item)=> { %>
                        <a href="<%= item.href %>" class="s-link <%= isActive(item) ? 'active' : '' %>">
                            <span class="s-link-label-full <%= item.shortLabel ? 'is-long' : '' %>">
                                <%= item.label %>
                            </span>
                            <% if (item.shortLabel) { %>
                                <span class="s-link-label-short">
                                    <%= item.shortLabel %>
                                </span>
                                <% } %>
                        </a>
                        <% }) %>
                </nav>

                <div class="s-actions">
                    <span class="s-badge">Tài khoản học viên</span>

                    <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/profile') %>" class="s-profile" aria-label="Mở hồ sơ học viên">
                        <div class="s-profile-meta">
                            <strong>
                                <%= safeStudentName %>
                            </strong>
                            <span>Đang học TOEIC online</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="s-avatar">
                            <%= studentInitial %>
                        </span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="<%= buildHref('/logout') %>" class="s-logout">Đăng xuất</a>

                    <a href="<%= buildHref('/logout') %>" class="s-logout-quick" aria-label="Đăng xuất">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M15 3h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-3"></path>
                            <path d="M10 17l5-5-5-5"></path>
                            <path d="M15 12H4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Thoát</span>
                    </a>

                    <button type="button" class="s-menu" id="studentMenuToggle" aria-label="Mở menu">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M4 7H20"></path>
                            <path d="M4 12H20"></path>
                            <path d="M4 17H20"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="s-mobile" id="studentMobilePanel">
                <div class="s-mobile-inner">
                    <div class="s-mobile-account">
                        <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/profile') %>" class="s-mobile-profile" aria-label="M&#7903; h&#7891; s&#417; h&#7885;c vi&#234;n">
                            <span class="s-avatar">
                                <%= studentInitial %>
                            </span>
                            <span class="s-mobile-profile-copy">
                                <strong><%= safeStudentName %></strong>
                                <span>T&#224;i kho&#7843;n h&#7885;c vi&#234;n TOEIC</span>
                            </span>
                        </a>
                        <div class="s-mobile-actions">
                            <a href="<%= buildHref('/logout') %>" class="s-logout">&#272;&#259;ng xu&#7845;t</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <% navItems.forEach((item)=> { %>
                        <a href="<%= item.href %>" class="s-link <%= isActive(item) ? 'active' : '' %>">
                            <%= item.label %>
                        </a>
                        <% }) %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <% if (safeSuccessMessages.length || safeErrorMessages.length || safeInfoMessages.length) { %>
            <section class="s-flash">
                <% safeSuccessMessages.forEach((msg)=> { %>
                    <div class="s-flash-card success">
                        <%= msg %>
                    </div>
                    <% }) %>

                        <% safeErrorMessages.forEach((msg)=> { %>
                            <div class="s-flash-card error">
                                <%= msg %>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>

                                <% safeInfoMessages.forEach((msg)=> { %>
                                    <div class="s-flash-card info">
                                        <%= msg %>
                                    </div>
                                    <% }) %>
            </section>
            <% } %>

                <main class="s-stage"><%- content %></main>

                <footer class="s-footer">
                    <div class="s-footer-inner">
                        <div class="s-footer-grid">
                            <section class="s-footer-col">
                                <h3>Thầy Tài Toeic</h3>
                                <p class="lead">Thầy Tài Toeic đào tạo và luyện thi TOEIC. Chất lượng luôn là ưu tiên
                                    hàng đầu cho học viên.</p>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/feedback') %>">Quy định lớp học</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/contact') %>">Chính sách quyền riêng tư</a>
                            </section>

                            <section class="s-footer-col">
                                <h3>Khóa học</h3>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/courses') %>">Thư viện khóa học</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/courses') %>">Khóa học TOEIC A</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/courses') %>">Khóa học TOEIC B</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/register-course') %>">Lớp Tập Sự</a>
                            </section>

                            <section class="s-footer-col">
                                <h3>Liên hệ</h3>
                                <p><strong>Email:</strong> realtoeiccentral@gmail.com</p>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/contact') %>">Fanpage: Thầy Tài Toeic</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/feedback') %>">Cộng đồng học TOEIC Thầy Tài Toeic</a>
                                <a href="<%= buildHref('/student/courses') %>">Góc học tập TOEIC Speaking &amp;
                                    Writing</a>
                            </section>

                            <section class="s-footer-col">
                                <h3>Địa chỉ</h3>
                                <p><strong>Cs1:</strong> Hồ Tùng Mậu</p>
                                <p>ĐC: Số 17, Ngõ 20 Đường Hồ Tùng Mậu, Cầu Giấy</p>
                                <p><strong>Hotline:</strong> 0344772436</p>
